# Mirror Puzzle

<catsoop-section>Introduction</catsoop-section>

The aim of this puzzle is to make the image by using given puzzle pieces and their mirror reflections.

<catsoop-section>Materials Required</catsoop-section>

- Mirror Box
- 8 puzzle pieces

