<catsoop-section>What's Happening</catsoop-section>

You are seeing the magic of **light reflection**!

As you place puzzle pieces near the mirror, you will notice beautiful symmetrical images forming. This helps you understand how light reflects and how shapes and patterns behave when mirrored.

**Key concepts:**
- **Reflection** — Light bounces off the mirror surface
- **Symmetry** — The reflected image is a mirror copy of the original
- **Line of symmetry** — The mirror acts as a line of symmetry, creating two identical halves

